name: Face Biografi :I'm and Im-age #001
description:
Know Yourself, before the algorithm knows You better.
The main question throughout human history about 
the search for meaning and origin, now got its pragmatic form.
Humans compete with artificial intelligence and
algorithms to hijack human consciousness.

This work is a visual way to collect
collective consciousness to safeguard human sovereignty.
Me and You.
We and Them.
It is a binary to maintain the dignity of " "I'm and Im-age"

by : Galamz (Iniseum)
